Almost there:

"There is nothing that needs to be done in fontdb, you need to have some kind of fonts installed on your system. If you use fontconfig, it will deal with that, if you don't then paths like below should contain fonts

                self.load_fonts_dir("/usr/share/fonts/");
                self.load_fonts_dir("/usr/local/share/fonts/");

my guess is that you don't have any fonts installed that would suffice for lapce"

